Package com.jnape.palatable.lambda.lens

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Lens<S,T,A,B>
    An approximation of van Laarhoven lenses.
    Lens.Fixed<S,T,A,B,F extends Functor,FT extends Functor<T,F>,FB extends Functor<B,F>>
    A lens that has been fixed to a functor.
    Lens.Simple<S,A>
    A convenience type with a simplified type signature for common lenses with both unified "larger" values and unified "smaller" values.
    Lens.Simple.Fixed<S,A,F extends Functor,FS extends Functor<S,F>,FA extends Functor<A,F>>
    A convenience type with a simplified type signature for fixed simple lenses.
